title: PATCH PES 2016 v1.0 [TUN MAKERS]
description:
How to install :

1. Install "PATCH PES 2016 v1.0.exe"
2. Copy the "save" folder from "PATCH PES 2016 v1.0 SAVE" to "DocumentsKONAMI", overwrite if asked.
3. Run the game from TMP SELECTOR.exe
